{"tid":2077776,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美核武談判放中國國旗諷缺席","createTime":"2020-06-24T13:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:04:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7468955e3962008c8c3ddff97832bbe0d25dab26","tid":2077776,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:59:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200624/OOCBLJ6WDTHAFSSKKWACH3NXWY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200624%2FOOCBLJ6WDTHAFSSKKWACH3NXWY%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=ec29e306\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200624%2FOOCBLJ6WDTHAFSSKKWACH3NXWY%2F&h=56b9eb84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200624/OOCBLJ6WDTHAFSSKKWACH3NXWY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美核武談判放中國國旗諷缺席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H3DIWTUJ73NHQKC4OVGVZEJL3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH3DIWTUJ73NHQKC4OVGVZEJL3A.jpg&h=49184150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國判談代表貼出限制核武談判桌上擺中國國旗的照片，諷刺中國缺席。<br />\n<br />\n美國前日與俄羅斯就延長《新削減戰略武器條約》（New START）談判，美方代表在Twitter上載一張放有中國國旗、但沒有代表出現的談判桌照片，諷刺中國缺席，惹來中國強烈不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華揶揄「行為藝術」<br />\n<br />\n美國軍備控制特別代表比林斯利（Marshall Billingslea）在貼上。。。。。。。表在談判前將三個國家的國旗放在桌上拍照，然後在俄方代表到場前取走。<br />\n<br />\n中方事後反應強烈，外交部軍控司司長傅聰在比林斯利的推文下以英語留言反擊：「奇怪場面啊！未經中國批准就在談判桌展示中國國旗，到底你有多卑劣？」中國駐維也納外交使團也揶揄比林斯利的推文貼圖是「行為藝術」。<br />\n<br />\nNew START是美俄2010年簽署的裁減戰略武器條約，明年2月到期。美國。。。。。。。不會向中國施壓，指美國硬要中國參與是不切實際。<br />\n<br />\n法新社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MZVZ7D6YUWPFXLVUEAUH3URE5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMZVZ7D6YUWPFXLVUEAUH3URE5Y.jpg&h=dad26d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比林斯利（右）與美國空軍中將伯西爾在談判結束後見記者。"},{"pid":"f54cb0c53e60bc9aef78594909348758cb765bd7","tid":2077776,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"求核戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}